text: Thibodaux is a city in the U.S. state of Louisiana. It is the parish seat of Lafourche Parish. This is in the northwestern part of the parish. The population was 15,948 at the 2020 census. == References == Category:Settlements in Lafourche Parish, Louisiana Category:Cities in Louisiana Category:Parish seats in Louisiana Category:1830 establishments in the United States Category:1830s establishments in Louisiana
